    "In case there is no majority, i.e., all three coders classified the sentence differently, the assigned label is randomly chosen.",
    "This affects 5 sentences on level 1 and",
    "sentences on level 3.",
    "The binary classification of level 2 ensures that there is always a majority label.7 See https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/prompt-engineering for the guidelines.",
    "When asked for a definition of \"Fiscal Dominance\" ChatGPT replies accurately."
